ut further constraints on the\nfour-fermion couplings, an expectation value for the the Higgs field will\ntrigger the subsequent condensation of an isospin-triplet field.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Jul 2017 11:53:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 12 Apr 2018 13:39:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-09"}
